Ubuntu Unity Software Center Release Notes

Write release entries:

git log --format="%s" --cherry-pick --right-only 3.38.1... | grep -i -v trivial | grep -v Merge | sort | uniq
Add any user visible changes into data/appdata/org.ubuntuunity.software.appdata.xml.in

Generate NEWS file:
appstream-util appdata-to-news ../data/appdata/org.ubuntuunity.software.appdata.xml.in > NEWS

git commit -a -m "Release version 7.7-Alpha1"
git tag -s 7.7-Alpha1 -m "==== Version 7.7-Alpha1 ===="
<enter password>

ninja-build dist
git push --tags
git push

scp meson-dist/*.tar.xz rhughes@master.gnome.org:
ssh rhughes@master.gnome.org
ftpadmin install ubuntu-unity-software-center-*.tar.xz

Post release version bump in meson.build

git commit -a -m "trivial: Post release version bump"
git push
